    We are a group of university graduates want to give small buisnesses empowerment and help buisnesses get there digital identity so our community can grow.

    Our Mission

    Empower small and large buisnesses to become digital identities and to help grow the economy of pakistan.

    Our Plan

    Our plan is to give 1000 buisnesses digital identity till the end of this year and to help new buisnesses grow faster.

    Our Vision

    We see Pakistan in future where our buisnesses competing with forign buisnesses and growing and helping the economy.
